Add JobSail — Your Career Compass (Job Tracker AI)

Full-featured local-first Kanban job application tracker:
- 6-column Kanban board with drag & drop
- Resume file upload (PDF/DOCX, base64 inline)
- Soft-delete with Trash view + undo
- Archive system with restore
- Smart reminder bar with overdue detection
- 5 filters including follow-up time (Overdue/Due Today/This Week/This Month)
- Dashboard with 8 stats + resume performance
- Activity timeline per job
- Priority system, dark mode, import/export (JSON+CSV)
- PWA ready, works fully offline
- Minimizable add/edit modal with form state preservation
- vercel.json for Vercel deployment

